c: 12
v: 76
t: He started with their bags before his brotherВґs. and then produced it from his brotherВґs bag. In that way We devised a cunning scheme for Yusuf. He could not have held his brother according to the statutes of the King вЂ” only because Allah had willed it so. We raise the rank of anyone We will. Over everyone with knowledge is a Knower